epi-SPU.def: We calculate the sustainable pesticide use indicator by adjusting a country’s pesticide risk score (Tang et al. 2021) using pesticide application rates (Maggi et al. 2019) to balance food security with ecosystem health.
epi-SPU.name: Pesticides
epi-SPU.source: rce Tang et al. 2021; Maggi et al. 2019.
